Salvage your dignity and regroup the family to make a name for yourself in MONOPOLY: Schitt&rsquo;s Creek! Buy, sell, and trade memorable locations in this hilarious twist on the classic game where you can own Rosebud Motel, capitalize on Caf&eacute; Tropical, and other opportunities to bankrupt your little townie friends. Set up Improvements and Renovations to collect rent or move money with the Rose Family Car on your way to victory&hellip; because no one plans on losing, but this is kind of a different playing field.

